This tool is used to create the JSON used by the X4 Universe Generation Tool create by Celludriel (https://forum.egosoft.com/viewtopic.php?f=181&t=408787).

WARNING - This is a beta release and it is a work in progress.

The tool has 3 different editors. 

1. Map editor - this allows the creating of galaxy. The placement of clusters, their settings and how they are connected.
2. Job editor - allows the creation of jobs.
3. Economy editor - allows the SOMETHING of the economy. 


IMAGES 

Installation Requirements
- .Net Framework 4.6.1
- Java 1.8 JDK
 
.NET:
 
Java:
- Install the latest java 1.8 JDK (https://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html)
- Make sure java is working by opening command line and typing java --version

Download 


Thanks to Celludriel for tha massive amount of help provided for doing this tool and the generation tool that does all the hard work. 

Known Bugs:

The map editor does some stranges things when you change its size. 

Limitations:
 
- Highways are not possible
- Currently all gates are accelleration gates
- The current vanilla FactionLogic will not work with a custom galaxy a custom FactionLogic is being developed but not ready


If you have problems not being able to install using the click once installer check out the following url: 
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-gb/visualstudio/deployment/how-to-configure-the-clickonce-trust-prompt-behavior?view=vs-2015
